title: What Makes an Inverted Pentagram Satanic
description:
Taken from my supporter only videos, this video looks at what it is about the inverted pentagram which has made it associated with Satanism, but also why we find it in some churches.  

The video was edited by Thomas Wijnaendts van Resandt.
